                international flights and two hours before the scheduled departure time for domestic flights. Arrive
                at the airport at least 2 hours before your international flight's departure time and 90 minutes
                before your domestic flight's departure time. Check-in counters close one hour and 45 minutes before
                the scheduled departure time for international flights and 45 minutes for domestic flights.
            </p>

